{"tid":2043684,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考牌問題","createTime":"2020-05-30T14:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T10:06:55.000Z","uid":302623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c75ba323fab93201746fffee26c8bb1d9f462086","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"小弟一開始想學私家車自動波，駕駛表格填咗1A，宜家心郁郁想學+考棍波，可唔可以買學牌嘅時候填1，然後考棍波?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係一定要跟TD82填咗嘅1A去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695e18196023c3022fd38eeeb07fcb659db79470","tid":2043684,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔得"},{"pid":"e18f25682c5c041ec41a6424312de8aea1f58032","tid":2043684,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"我估買學牌可以買私家車棍, 但考試就唔得, 因為你買個張考試表格係考私家車自動波黎, 只可以考自動<br />\n<br />\n我諗你應該要打去運輸署問下有冇得改考棍波先, 之後臨考前2-3個月再搞學牌啦<br />\n<br />\n不過你都係考自動算喇, 易學易上手過棍波勁多, 絶對可以學少好多堂平多啲, 而且學少好多堂咪鬼益啲粗聲粗氣既教車佬咪幾好, 更何況如果你第日唔係要渣貨車揾食既話根本唔洗棍波<br />\n<br />\n利申：棍van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59fd9e2917bb8f4e1ec9b8ae978c75727d16fe3","tid":2043684,"uid":135703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"考完筆試後仲有最後機會轉"},{"pid":"43de5203f73dd137a6d87e0af3a2fecbb1dcf314","tid":2043684,"uid":127929,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"考自動算喇, 2020年喇, 而家除左渣貨車仲邊有人渣棍架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考自動架車唔洗chok下chok下咪幾好, 易上手, 可以上少幾堂慳2-3千蚊爽過打飛機喇"},{"pid":"43c2e9d5906b589e403b9fc5e694ff93dc4e33fb","tid":2043684,"uid":249304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"係轉就快，還店都係自動波，點解唔考自動van？貴小小但有齊1,2號牌，好過之後又要比錢再考"},{"pid":"a81a78ef00f6fe5457fb4625bf3587602011355b","tid":2043684,"uid":336015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"睇下你鐘意揸咩車 如果有興趣evo 掃把佬跑車就考棍  如果係普通腳車就自動都得  唔駛搞咁多野學咁多堂"},{"pid":"6d2a77326940c8875d135905f8d397dc82bb9cdf","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"但係點解td55填1最後可以考1A 但係掉返轉唔得?"},{"pid":"3d42d4ed662e422fdb820ff68831c11f4134cc87","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2a77326940c8875d135905f8d397dc82bb9cdf","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"但係點解td55填1最後可以考1A 但係掉返轉唔得?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"on9咗<br />\n應該係td82"},{"pid":"b8ea88d3b8093a5f0858ce997aaf2dcaa0c5a366","tid":2043684,"uid":13993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d42d4ed662e422fdb820ff68831c11f4134cc87","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2a77326940c8875d135905f8d397dc82bb9cdf","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"但係點解td55填1最後可以考1A 但係掉返轉唔得?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:04:27.000Z","msg":"on9咗<br />\n應該係td82"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"考棍送自動<br />\n其實一係棍van或自動波van抵考啲，而且又多鏡，泊車調頭都易啲"},{"pid":"b94cf2f38d65beaed4273ff9522d257561db904c","tid":2043684,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ea88d3b8093a5f0858ce997aaf2dcaa0c5a366","tid":2043684,"uid":13993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d42d4ed662e422fdb820ff68831c11f4134cc87","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2a77326940c8875d135905f8d397dc82bb9cdf","tid":2043684,"uid":302623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"但係點解td55填1最後可以考1A 但係掉返轉唔得?"}